      <title>安装oh-my-posh</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/24/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85oh-my-posh/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/24/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85oh-my-posh/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="下载PowerShell"><a href="#下载PowerShell" class="headerlink" title="下载PowerShell"></a>下载PowerShell</h2><p><a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/zh-cn/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell-on-windows?view=powershell-7.3#msi">点击下载</a><br>然后在Windows terminal下设置为默认启动配置</p><hr><h2 id="下载oh-my-posh"><a href="#下载oh-my-posh" class="headerlink" title="下载oh-my-posh"></a>下载oh-my-posh</h2><p>微软商店下直接搜索下载即可<br><a href="https://apps.microsoft.com/store/detail/ohmyposh/XP8K0HKJFRXGCK">点击下载</a></p><hr><h2 id="配置-美化oh-my-posh"><a href="#配置-美化oh-my-posh" class="headerlink" title="配置/美化oh-my-posh"></a>配置/美化oh-my-posh</h2><p>首先安装几个插件，PowerShell中运行命令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Install-Module posh-git -Scope CurrentUser</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装文件图标库</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Install-Module -Name Terminal-Icons -Repository PSGallery</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后修改配置文件，运行命令，会提示创建一个文件，确认即可：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">notepad.exe $PROFILE</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在文本中粘贴：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Import-Module posh-git</span><br><span class="line">oh-my-posh init pwsh --config ~/.powerlevel10k_rainbow.omp.json | Invoke-Expression</span><br><span class="line">Import-Module -Name Terminal-Icons</span><br><span class="line">Set-PSReadlineKeyHandler -Key Tab -Function MenuComplete</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里的powerlevel10k_rainbow是主题。主题可以在C:\Users\insis\AppData\Local\Programs\oh-my-posh\themes下找到，想换什么主题可以自己选，具体主题可以参考<a href="https://ohmyposh.dev/docs/themes">官网</a></p><hr><h2 id="其他"><a href="#其他" class="headerlink" title="其他"></a>其他</h2><p>有些主题需要安装字体，<a href="https://www.nerdfonts.com/font-downloads">下载</a><br>选择Caskaydia Core Nerd Font下载，解压后安装其中的</p><h6 id="Caskaydia-Cove-Nerd-Font-Complete-Mono-Light"><a href="#Caskaydia-Cove-Nerd-Font-Complete-Mono-Light" class="headerlink" title="Caskaydia Cove Nerd Font Complete Mono Light"></a>Caskaydia Cove Nerd Font Complete Mono Light</h6><p>或</p><h6 id="Caskaydia-Cove-Nerd-Font-Complete-Mono-Windows-Compatible-Light"><a href="#Caskaydia-Cove-Nerd-Font-Complete-Mono-Windows-Compatible-Light" class="headerlink" title="Caskaydia Cove Nerd Font Complete Mono Windows Compatible Light"></a>Caskaydia Cove Nerd Font Complete Mono Windows Compatible Light</h6><p>字体。自己选择即可</p><hr><p>##参考资料：<br><a href="https://gist.github.com/xiaopeng163/0fe4225a56ff97cd47e25a4b8a6f36ec">https://gist.github.com/xiaopeng163/0fe4225a56ff97cd47e25a4b8a6f36ec</a><br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV12u411Z7Zo/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_history.content.click&amp;vd_source=21c2f1a3bb54ecc54b638fa6f1716428">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV12u411Z7Zo/?spm_id_from=333.1007.top_right_bar_window_history.content.click&amp;vd_source=21c2f1a3bb54ecc54b638fa6f1716428</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/m0_56069948/article/details/124909176?spm=1001.2101.3001.6661.1&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~Rate-1-124909176-blog-124950605.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv3&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2~default~CTRLIST~Rate-1-124909176-blog-124950605.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv3&amp;utm_relevant_index=1">https://blog.csdn.net/m0_56069948/article/details/124909176?spm=1001.2101.3001.6661.1&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7ECTRLIST%7ERate-1-124909176-blog-124950605.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv3&amp;depth_1-utm_source=distribute.pc_relevant_t0.none-task-blog-2%7Edefault%7ECTRLIST%7ERate-1-124909176-blog-124950605.pc_relevant_multi_platform_whitelistv3&amp;utm_relevant_index=1</a><br><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/Likianta/article/details/124950605">https://blog.csdn.net/Likianta/article/details/124950605</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
