      <title>安装zsh</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/24/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85zsh/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/24/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85zsh/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安装zsh"><a href="#安装zsh" class="headerlink" title="安装zsh"></a>安装zsh</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入密码后自动安装，按Y确认<br>安装完成后输入命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>即可使用</p><p>先退出</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">q</span><br><span class="line">exit</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开浏览器，访问：<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh">https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh</a><br>通过curl或wget命令在shell中执行，这里选择curl</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/master/tools/install.sh)&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可能碰到网络原因安装不上，可以试试vpn<br>命令执行后按y表示切换zsh为默认shell。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时我们就完成了zsh的安装</p><h2 id="配置zsh（oh-my-zsh）"><a href="#配置zsh（oh-my-zsh）" class="headerlink" title="配置zsh（oh-my-zsh）"></a>配置zsh（oh-my-zsh）</h2><p>我们可以安装不同的plugins插件或者theme主题，来帮我们完成配置和美化效果<br>插件：访问：<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Plugins">https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Plugins</a><br>主题：访问：<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes">https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes</a><br>这里是<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh#using-oh-my-zsh">插件使用说明</a><br>可以自行选择插件和主题，介绍一下zsh内置的plugin<br>终端中输入</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd .oh-my-zsh</span><br><span class="line">ls</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>会发现在zsh目录下有个plugins文件夹，这就是内置的插件<br>我们cd进去</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd plugins</span><br><span class="line">ls</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以看到有很多内置插件<br>使用这些插件只需要修改配置文件<br>修改配置文件需要回到用户根目录。新开一个终端即可<br>然后新终端中输入：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到<br>将需要的插件名称加入括号内即可，如：</p><p>这里添加了minikube插件，该插件具体作用可以查看<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Plugins">官方说明</a>下的<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/tree/master/plugins/minikube">minikube</a><br>该插件主要用来补全命令行的<br>除了官方插件外还可以添加第三方插件，推荐一个<a href="https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions">zsh-autosuggestions</a><br>食用方法，回到我们之前的终端（也就是在plugins目录下的）<br>执行命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样就把该插件( zsh-autosuggestions )安装下来了，使用方法和之前的minikube一样，也是添加到配置文件即可生效</p><p>可以通过重启终端或者执行下列代码让配置生效</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这时我们就能看到效果了</p><p>灰色表示之前的命令，可以按方向键右键补全，虽说原版按上下键也能做到，但这样更直观更方便了</p><hr><h2 id="安装主题"><a href="#安装主题" class="headerlink" title="安装主题"></a>安装主题</h2><p>也是和安装插件一样，修改为想要的主题名称即可，可以在<a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes">官方主题</a>看到预览截图<br>进入配置文件的命令</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim ~/.zshrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以自行研究主题</p><hr><p>参考资料：<br>oh-my-zsh <a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh">https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh</a><br>oh-my-zsh plugins <a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Plugins">https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Plugins</a><br>oh-my-zsh theme <a href="https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes">https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/wiki/Themes</a><br>zsh-autosuggestions <a href="https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions">https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions</a></p><p><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1sv41147FS/?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0&amp;vd_source=21c2f1a3bb54ecc54b638fa6f1716428">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1sv41147FS/?spm_id_from=333.999.0.0&amp;vd_source=21c2f1a3bb54ecc54b638fa6f1716428</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
